    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20-Holiday-Gift-Programs-that-Benefit-Nonprofits.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-20394\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20-Holiday-Gift-Programs-that-Benefit-Nonprofits-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" alt=\"20-holiday-gift-programs-that-benefit-nonprofits\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20-Holiday-Gift-Programs-that-Benefit-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20-Holiday-Gift-Programs-that-Benefit-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20-Holiday-Gift-Programs-that-Benefit-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=768%2C768&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20-Holiday-Gift-Programs-that-Benefit-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20-Holiday-Gift-Programs-that-Benefit-Nonprofits.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/20-Holiday-Gift-Programs-that-Benefit-Nonprofits.jpg?w=800&amp;ssl=1 800w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>For environmentally friendly and socially conscious holiday shoppers that prefer to give donations to nonprofits as holiday gifts, the 20 holiday gift programs listed below are a good starting point for your holiday shopping. Ranging from wildlife conservation to refugee relief, tribute gifts make excellent holiday gifts for friends, family, and work colleagues. If you prefer to give traditional gifts, you can also shop for good at <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2016/11/04/30-online-stores-that-benefit-nonprofits/\"><strong>30 online stores that benefit nonprofits</strong></a>. Either way, put your consumer spending power to work fostering social good this holiday season.</p>\n<hr />\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Audubon Society Gift Catalog<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.audubon.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://store.audubon.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-20304 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Audubon-Society.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"audubon-society\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Audubon-Society.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Audubon-Society.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">2. Best Friends Animal Society Gifts<br />\n<a href=\"http://bestfriends.org/symbolic-charitable-gifts-pet-lovers\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://bestfriends.org/symbolic-charitable-gifts-pet-lovers\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20326\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/BFAS.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"bfas\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/BFAS.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/BFAS.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">3. charity: water Donation Cards<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.donorschoose.org/donors/giftoptions.html\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://store.charitywater.org/products/gift-card\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20319\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/charity-water.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"charity-water\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/charity-water.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/charity-water.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">4. DonorsChoose.org Gift Cards<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.donorschoose.org/donors/giftoptions.html\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.donorschoose.org/donors/giftoptions.html\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20364\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/donorschoose.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"donorschoose\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/donorschoose.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/donorschoose.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">5. Global Giving Gift Cards<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/gifts/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.globalgiving.org/gifts/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-20329 size-full\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Gloabl-Giving.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"gloabl-giving\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Gloabl-Giving.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Gloabl-Giving.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">6. Heifer International Gift Catalog<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.heifer.org/gift-catalog/holiday/index.html\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.heifer.org/gift-catalog/holiday/index.html\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20341\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Heifer-International.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"heifer-international\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Heifer-International.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Heifer-International.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">7. International Rescue Committee Gifts<br />\n<a href=\"http://gifts.rescue.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://gifts.rescue.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20343\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/IRC-Gifts.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"irc-gifts\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/IRC-Gifts.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/IRC-Gifts.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">8. National Wildlife Federation Gifts<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.shopnwf.org/Adoption-Center\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.shopnwf.org/Adoption-Center\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20346\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/NWF-Gifts.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"nwf-gifts\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/NWF-Gifts.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/NWF-Gifts.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">9. Nature Conservancy Gift Catalog<br />\n<a href=\"http://gifts.nature.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://gifts.nature.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20351\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Natiure-Conservancy-Gifts.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"natiure-conservancy-gifts\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Natiure-Conservancy-Gifts.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Natiure-Conservancy-Gifts.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">10. Nothing But Nets Gift Nets<br />\n<a href=\"https://secure.globalproblems-globalsolutions.org/site/SPageNavigator/NBN_fall_2016_api.html\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://secure.globalproblems-globalsolutions.org/site/SPageNavigator/NBN_fall_2016_api.html\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20352\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Nothing-But-Nets.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"nothing-but-nets\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Nothing-But-Nets.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Nothing-But-Nets.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 class=\"content-title\" style=\"text-align: center;\">11. Oceana Marine Wildlife Adoptions<br />\n<a href=\"https://gift.oceana.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://gift.oceana.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20353\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Oceana.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"oceana\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Oceana.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Oceana.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 class=\"content-title\" style=\"text-align: center;\">12. Orangutan Outreach Adoptions<br />\n<a href=\"https://redapes.org/adopt\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://redapes.org/adopt\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20312\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Orangutan-Outreach-Adotpions.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"orangutan-outreach-adotpions\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Orangutan-Outreach-Adotpions.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Orangutan-Outreach-Adotpions.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">13. Oxfam Gifts<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.oxfamgifts.com/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.oxfamgifts.com