;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/snowleopard.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">19. UNICEF Inspired Gifts<br />\n<a href=\"https://inspiredgifts.unicefusa.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://inspiredgifts.unicefusa.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20370\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/unicef-gifts.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"unicef-gifts\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/unicef-gifts.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/unicef-gifts.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">20. Women for Women International Gifts<br />\n<a href=\"http://gifts.womenforwomen.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20336\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/Give-Now-Buttin.jpg?resize=145%2C40\" alt=\"give-now-buttin\" width=\"145\" height=\"40\" /></a></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://gifts.womenforwomen.org/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-20371\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/women.png?resize=600%2C364\" alt=\"women\" width=\"600\" height=\"364\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/women.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/women.png?resize=300%2C182&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 17px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;\"><em>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</em></span></span></strong></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-16887 alignleft\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/10/mobile-for-good-with-ribbon.jpg?resize=99%2C150\" alt=\"mobile for good with ribbon\" width=\"99\" height=\"150\" /></a>Based on more than 20 years of experience and 25,000+ hours spent utilizing mobile and social media, <a href=\"http://www.amazon.com/Mobile-Good-How--Fundraising-Nonprofits/dp/0071825460\" target=\"_blank\"><em><strong>Mobile for Good: A How-To Fundraising Guide for Nonprofits</strong></em></a> is a comprehensive 256-page book packed with more than 500 best practices. Written on the premise that all communications and fundraising are now mobile and social, Mobile for Good is a step-by-step how-to guide for writing, implementing, and maintaining a mobile and social fundraising strategy for your nonprofit.</p>\n",
